{
  "title": "Smoky Vanilla Greek Yogurt Mousse",
  "description": "A velvety, smoky-vanilla Greek yogurt mousse that's both sweet and slightly tart, perfect for a quick dessert or luscious snack.",
  "cuisine": "Greek",
  "diet": [
    "halal",
